SystemColumn.Formula:
IF( [Status] = "Requested",
"Requested / "& EBMS_GET_ROLE_DISPLAYNAME([Assignee]),
"Acknowledged / "&[Acknowledged By Nice Name] & " (" & DATEFORMAT([Date of Event], "dd-MMM-yyyy") & ")" )

Column.Name: Acknowledged By Nice Name
Column.Formula: IF( AND( [Acknowledged By]!=NULL(), [Acknowledged on behalf of] != NULL(), [Acknowledged By] != [Acknowledged on behalf of] ), EBMS_GET_ROLE_DISPLAYNAME([Acknowledged on behalf of])&" ("&EBMS_GET_ROLE_DISPLAYNAME([Acknowledged By])&")", EBMS_GET_ROLE_DISPLAYNAME([Acknowledged By]) )

Column.Name: Type
Column.Formula: LET $parent := EBMS_GET_PARENT_RECORD(EFormType, RecordID); RETURN DB_LOOKUP("Document", "Document", HASH("RecordID", ARRAY_LAST($parent)))
